Package com.plasmoxy.cvfxbase Description

Welcome, traveler !
This is Javadoc for my CVFXBase Java package.

CVFXBase is an OpenCV JavaFX extensible application with various controls and 3 views. It includes an interface for easy OpenCV programming.
I created it to quickly and easily setup a GUI and OpenCV renderer and focus on OpenCV logic.
